				<h3> Re: BEP-RFC.  Verifying the author of a .torrent file (verified torrents).</h3>
				<div class="postmsg">
					<p>Also see <a href="http://forum.bittorrent.org/viewtopic.php?id=166" rel="nofollow">http://forum.bittorrent.org/viewtopic.php?id=166</a><br /><br />Bobbin(1) has a working test implementation of both a signature metadata extension and growing torrents. The signature algorithm used is currently DSA rather than RSA, mainly on the basis that it produces small, fixed size (40 byte) signatures.<br /><br />A standard for this would be welcome.<br /><br />(1) <a href="http://code.google.com/p/bobbin/" rel="nofollow">http://code.google.com/p/bobbin/</a></p>
