					<p>When using magnets, only the info-dict is transferred, so your &quot;encrypted_info_hash&quot; would not be included, this feature would be limited to uses with access to the full torrent-file.<br /><br />However you could get around this by just signing the &quot;pieces&quot;+&quot;piece length&quot;, and have the &quot;author_key&quot; and signature in the info dict..</p>
