				<h3> Re: BEP-RFC.  Verifying the author of a .torrent file (verified torrents).</h3>
				<div class="postmsg">
					<p>I see an issue with adding new keys to the info dict. The existence of several swarms (infohashes) describing the same content is already a problem today, adding more variables to the info dict only makes this problem worse.<br /><br />Instead of bulky RSA signatures i'd suggest a Curve25519 signature in outside the info dict, this could easily be added to magnet links.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="postsignature"><hr />Az dev</div>
